answer:
If $x = \angle BAC$, then $\angle BDC = 3x$ and $\angle BDM = 2x$.  Also, $\angle BMD = 90^\circ$, so $\angle MBD = 90^\circ - 2x$.  Similarly, $\angle MCB = 90^\circ - x$.

[asy]
unitsize(0.4 cm);

pair A, B, C, D, M;

A = (0,11);
D = (0,1);
B = (-11/2,0);
C = (11/2,0);
